{"published time": "2024-03-31T07:37:00+08:00", "images": ["https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/featured-2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/land-day-palestine.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003-2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Chile3003.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-1024x576.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-2-1024x576.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine-2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ljubljana.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"513\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/featured-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/featured-2.webp\" width=\"770\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <p>\n  <em>\n   Featured image: Kites flying over Rafah amid plumes of smoke. Source: Al Jazeera\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p>\n  The Land Day, Yom-al-Ard, was celebrated for the 48\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  time in Palestine and among the Palestinian diaspora all over the world on the 30\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March to commemorate protests against Israel confiscating 2,000 hectares of Palestinian lands in 1976. In these protests, six Palestinians were murdered and over a 100 were injured by the Israeli Forces. Meanwhile, Israel continues the genocide in Gaza, with over 32,700 people massacred.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10407\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"513\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/land-day-palestine.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/land-day-palestine.webp\" width=\"770\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    <br/>\n    A rally in Bethlehem, occupied West Bank for the 48\n    <sup>\n     th\n    </sup>\n    Land Day. Source: Al Jazeera\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Deir Hanna, in the north of annexed Palestine, a demonstration was held for the Land Day\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Palestinians?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Palestinians\n     </a>\n     in the village of Deir Hanna in northern occupied Palestine held a demonstration on the occasion of Land Day.\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     They chanted: \"Gaza of Hashem does not bow to the tank and cannon!\"\n     <br/>\n     \"O\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gaza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Gaza\n     </a>\n     , steadfast, steadfast! From your land the lions emerged!\"\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     The head of the\u2026\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/TZugEVbaWE\">\n      pic.twitter.com/TZugEVbaWE\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 The Resistance (@TopGResistance)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TopGResistance/status/1774108318186746015?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 30, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Despite in words calling for \u201crestraint\u201d in Gaza and for the first time not vetoing a UN resolution calling for an immediate ceasefire to Gaza, the US\n  <a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/3/30/us-approves-bombs-jets-for-israel-amid-threat-of-offensive-in-gazas-rafah\">\n   has authorized\n  </a>\n  <em>\n   $2.5bn\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   worth of war planes and bombs to be transferred to Israel. The package includes more than 1,800 MK84 2,000-pound bombs and 500 MK82 500-pound bombs.\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   Th\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   is\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   type of bombs can cause destruction in a radius of hundreds of meters and are linked to earlier bombings with high number of civilian casualties in Gaza.\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p>\n  Last Thursday, the International Court of Justice\n  <a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/icj-orders-israel-to-act-on-aid-crisis-in-gaza-palestinian-authority-names-new-cabinet/ar-BB1kFQnC\">\n   made a new order\n  </a>\n  again calling Israel to \u201ctake all necessary and effective measures\u201d to ensure the entry of aid into Gaza. After the original ICJ order, the amount of aid let in by Israel has decreased, and Israel has shown no signs of respecting the court order. On the 24\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March Israel\n  <a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/israel-blocks-unrwa-s-food-convoys-from-entering-starving-north-gaza/ar-BB1kvFMh\">\n   openly told the UN\n  </a>\n  that it will not be allowing UNRWA aid convoys to enter northern Gaza. UNRWA is the main agency providing aid in Gaza, and its funding has already been cut by many imperialists due to Israeli allegations. We have earlier written on Israel using famine as a weapon\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/19/gaza-famine-is-imminent/\">\n   here\n  </a>\n  and on its crimes against humanity\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/23/crimes-of-israel/\">\n   here.\n  </a>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In addition, Israel\n  <a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/israel-hits-syria-in-heaviest-raid-on-iran-proxies-in-months/ar-BB1kLAZY\">\n   carried out air strikes\n  </a>\n  in the Aleppo province of Syria, killing at least six Hezbollah fighters and at least 33 Syrian civilians. Dozens have also been injured, some seriously. This is the deadliest attack by Israel on Syria since October 7\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  .\n </p>\n <p>\n  The IDF is carrying out a military operation in the al-Shifa hospital complex, where 30,000 displaced Palestinians, medical staff and patients were trapped as of the 18\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March, and is facing fierce\n  <a href=\"https://www.palestinechronicle.com/back-to-khan-yunis-resistance-roundup-day-175/\">\n   resistance\n  </a>\n  from the Heroic Palestinian National Resistance Front, which is among other things bombarding the enemy with mortar shells in the vicinity of the hospital. Multiple clashes have been reported. Al-Qassam Brigades has reported on the 29\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March having targeted Israeli Merkava tanks, destroying one completely. They have also clashed with a group of IDF soldiers barricaded inside a building, killing and wounding multiple of them in the vicinity of the al-Shifa hospital. Multiple IDF soldiers were wounded and killed also near Nasser hospital near Khan Younis. Al-Quds Brigades report they have wounded and killed IDF soldiers in an ambush west of Khan Younis. Israeli sources report that a sergeant major of the IDF was killed and 16 other soldiers were wounded on Friday in Gaza. On the border to Lebanon, Hezbollah continues carrying out air strikes against Israel.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Meanwhile, peoples of the world continue calling for the end of the genocide and showing solidarity with the struggle of the Palestinian people.\n </p>\n <p>\n  A massive demonstration in Jordan, in front of the Israeli embassy to protest against the Israel crimes in Palestine\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     \ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf4\ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\uddf8Demonstration in support of\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Palestine?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Palestine\n     </a>\n     in front of the\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Israeli?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Israeli\n     </a>\n     embassy in\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Amman?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Amman\n     </a>\n     in\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Jordan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Jordan\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SaveGaza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #SaveGaza\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/StopGazaGenocide?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #StopGazaGenocide\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gaza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Gaza\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GazaHolocaust?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #GazaHolocaust\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IsraelTerrorist?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #IsraelTerrorist\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IsraelCrimes?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #IsraelCrimes\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CeasefireNOW?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #CeasefireNOW\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gaza_life_matters?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Gaza_life_matters\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GazaFamine?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #GazaFamine\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/PalestineLivesMatter?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #PalestineLivesMatter\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Jordans?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Jordans\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/ErdazlgryQ\">\n      pic.twitter.com/ErdazlgryQ\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 Gabriele M. (@Gabriele_M24)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Gabriele_M24/status/1773834917819904378?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 29, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     Press coverage \u201cOh\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Amman?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Amman\n     </a>\n     , this is coming.\u201d A massive demonstration near the Israeli occupation embassy in Jordan. Support for\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gaza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Gaza\n     </a>\n     .\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Palestine?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Palestine\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Jordan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Jordan\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/lnHDY66fkA\">\n      pic.twitter.com/lnHDY66fkA\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 Siraj Noorani (@sirajnoorani)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sirajnoorani/status/1773816112209387958?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 29, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Casablanca, Morocco, another demonstration took place:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"rtl\" lang=\"ar\">\n     \u0645\u0638\u0627\u0647\u0631\u0629 \u062d\u0627\u0634\u062f\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0627\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0636\u0627\u0621 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0645\u063a\u0631\u0628 \u0631\u0641\u0636\u0627 \u0644\u0644\u062d\u0631\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u062a\u0645\u0631\u0629 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0642\u0637\u0627\u0639 \u063a\u0632\u0629.\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%D8%B7%D9%88%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%AA_%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B5%D9%89?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #\u0637\u0648\u0641\u0627\u062a_\u0627\u0644\u0627\u0642\u0635\u0649\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #\u0627\u0644\u0645\u063a\u0631\u0628\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/oGeppgpkeY\">\n      pic.twitter.com/oGeppgpkeY\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 \u0634\u0628\u0643\u0629 \u0623\u0635\u062f\u0642\u0627\u0621 \u0641\u0644\u0633\u0637\u064a\u0646 (@fopnetwork_ar)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fopnetwork_ar/status/1773969523168665845?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 30, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Also in the city of Tangier, Morocco on 25th of March:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"rtl\" lang=\"ar\">\n     \u0645\u0638\u0627\u0647\u0631\u0629 \u0643\u0628\u064a\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u062f\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u0637\u0646\u062c\u0629 \u0634\u0645\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u063a\u0631\u0628 \u062f\u0639\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0641\u0644\u0633\u0637\u064a\u0646 \u0648\u0631\u0641\u0636\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0644\u0639\u062f\u0648\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0633\u0631\u0627\u0626\u064a\u0644\u064a \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u063a\u0632\u0629\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%D9%81%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%B7%D9%8A%D9%86?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #\u0641\u0644\u0633\u0637\u064a\u0646\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/29IFJzBr0L\">\n      pic.twitter.com/29IFJzBr0L\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 palgraph (@palestine_graph)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/palestine_graph/status/1772425495872680096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 26, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In the city of\n  <a href=\"https://en.abna24.com/story/1446621\">\n   Qom\n  </a>\n  , in Iran, a huge demonstration took place to condemn the recent crimes of the Zionists.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10416\" data-id=\"10416\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"600\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003.webp\" width=\"900\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10417\" data-id=\"10417\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/qom3003-2.webp\" width=\"900\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Demonstration in Qom. Source: ABNA24\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  On 28th of March, a demonstration in Cairo, Egypt took place outside the journalist syndicate. The march was called by the syndicate itself and chants as \u201cLiberation with a riffle\u201d were shouted.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     A demonstration by the Journalists Syndicate and chants of \u201cPalestine is Arab\u201d and \u201cliberation with a rifle.\u201d Abu Ubaida, tell people, the international community is a coward in Cairo right now\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AbuObeida?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #AbuObeida\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/egypt?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #egypt\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/cairo?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #cairo\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreedomPalestine?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #FreedomPalestine\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/demonstration?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #demonstration\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/zGREgcwMoB\">\n      pic.twitter.com/zGREgcwMoB\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 Gaza news\ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\uddf8SM (@al_melgy75828)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/al_melgy75828/status/1772691955694051573?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 26, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  This week, another demonstration took place in the Matareya neighborhood, also in Cairo:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     Egypt,from the centre of Cairo in Matareya neighborhood\n     <br/>\n     -a group break fast became a demonstration in support to Palestine and \"Gaza\"\n     <br/>\n     -\"by our souls,bloods we will sacrifice for you,O Palestine\"\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/5m98u1Hfn6\">\n      pic.twitter.com/5m98u1Hfn6\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 \u0623\u0645\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u0633\u0644\u0645\u0629 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0629 (@AmtRbyt95298)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AmtRbyt95298/status/1772658253253480455?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 26, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In the capital city of Yemen, Sanaa, a huge demonstration took place to support the people of Palestine.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">\n     \ud83d\udfe5 Manifestation d'un million de personnes dans la capitale y\u00e9m\u00e9nite,\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Sanaa?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Sanaa\n     </a>\n     , en soutien \u00e0\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gaza?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #Gaza\n     </a>\n     , le vendredi de \"Nous entrons dans la dixi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e, et la Palestine est notre premi\u00e8re cause\".\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/WiJ8GdvQWM\">\n      pic.twitter.com/WiJ8GdvQWM\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 \ud83d\udd3bMedzfight\ud83c\udf49 (@medzfight)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/medzfight/status/1773875297881887083?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 30, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Tokyo, Japan, a demonstration was done in front of the train station of Shinjuku.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"zxx\">\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/SCzb36rITc\">\n      pic.twitter.com/SCzb36rITc\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 \u51a8\u6c38\u660c\u656c (@dolvic2002)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dolvic2002/status/1773965090615853320?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 30, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  On March 23rd in Quito, Ecuador, a demonstration in solidarity with Palestine took place.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"es\">\n     Marcha en solidaridad con Palestina \ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\uddf8 en Quito-Ecuador\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreePalestina?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #FreePalestina\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/nlvNO7HZM6\">\n      pic.twitter.com/nlvNO7HZM6\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 @atipak (@atipak)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/atipak/status/1771728132065698054?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 24, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  In\n  <a href=\"https://en.abna24.com/story/1445248https://en.abna24.com/story/1445248\">\n   Chile\n  </a>\n  , a massive demonstration took place in the streets of Santiago de Chile to demand the immediate ceasefire in the Gaza Strip.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10408\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"558\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Chile3003.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Chile3003.webp\" width=\"1000\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Massive demonstration in Chile. Source: ABNA24\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In\n  <a href=\"https://en.abna24.com/story/1446869\">\n   San Francisco\n  </a>\n  , in United States, a massive demonstration took place. The demonstration demanded the stop of the financing of Israel by the US.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10418\" data-id=\"10418\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-1024x576.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-1024x576.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10419\" data-id=\"10419\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-2-1024x576.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sanfrancisco3003-2-1024x576.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Demonstration in San Francisco, USA. Source: ABNA24\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In London, protesters\n  <a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/watch-pro-palestinian-protesters-occupy-department-for-business-and-trade/ar-BB1kIaTG\">\n   occupied\n  </a>\n  the government Department for Business and Trade on Friday morning and denounced its links to arming Israel.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10414\" data-id=\"10414\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"478\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-1.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10415\" data-id=\"10415\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/london-2.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Protesters occupying the Department for Business and Trade in London. Source: The Telegraph\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Berlin,\n  <a href=\"https://www.yenisafak.com/en/news/berlin-police-crack-down-on-pro-palestinian-demonstrators-assault-woman-3680401\">\n   protesters organized\n  </a>\n  a sit-in at a staircase at the Berlin Central Station on Friday the 29\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  , shouting slogans for the freedom of Palestine. The police repressed the protest, and arrested and beat up protesters claiming they were shouting \u201dbanned\u201d slogans.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">\n     Update: 16:50\n     <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/b2903?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n      #b2903\n     </a>\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/C6BB2qnWyT\">\n      pic.twitter.com/C6BB2qnWyT\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    \u2014 Iman Sefati (@ISefati)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ISefati/status/1773740537192874252?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 29, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Greece, a military parade for the national day of Greece\n  <a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-ae/news/other/palestine-activists-obstruct-greece-military-parade-for-gaza/ar-BB1kyIrH\">\n   was briefly disrupted\n  </a>\n  by protesters who ran in front of a tank waving Palestinian flags.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/plDU7DvMkjA?feature=oembed\" title=\"Pro-Palestinian protesters obstruct Greece military parade | #AJshorts\" width=\"1140\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  In Valkeakoski, Finland, ICL posters supporting the heroic national resistance of the Palestinian people\n  <a href=\"https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2024/03/27/pirkanmaa-julisteita-ja-tarroja-valkeakoskella/\">\n   were put up\n  </a>\n  .\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n   <figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10420\" data-id=\"10420\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"709\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine.webp\" width=\"524\"/>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10421\" data-id=\"10421\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"703\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/valkeakoski-palestine-2.webp\" width=\"525\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Posters have been put up in the town of Valkeakoski in Finland. Source: Punalippu\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Copenhagen, Denmark slogans\n  <a href=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/29/kobenhavn-solidaritetsaktioner-for-det-palaestinensiske-folk-fortsaetter/\">\n   have been painted.\n  </a>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10409\" data-id=\"10409\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-1.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10410\" data-id=\"10410\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/copenhagen-2.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   <br/>\n   Slogans \u201cLong live Palestine!\u201d and \u201cFree the political prisoner Georges Abdallah!\u201d have been painted in Copenhagen. Source: Socialistisk Revolution.\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Ljubljana, Slovenia, an event attended by the European Parliament President Roberta Metsola\n  <a href=\"https://www.aa.com.tr/en/europe/pro-palestinian-protesters-interrupt-program-attended-by-european-parliament-head-in-slovenian-capital/3176640#\">\n   was disrupted\n  </a>\n  by protesters demanding action to stop the genocide Israel is carrying out in Gaza. \u201cStop genocide in Gaza! Sanction Israel now!\u201d they shouted.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\">\n  <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10413\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"486\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ljubljana.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ljubljana.webp\" width=\"864\"/>\n  <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n   Protesters unfurled Palestinian flags and shouted slogans against the genocide in Gaza. Source: Anadolu Ajans\u0131\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n</div>", "pdf_content": "", "pdf_links": [], "source": "https://redherald.org/2024/03/30/us-approves-new-delivery-of-bombs-and-war-planes-to-israel-amid-protests/", "type": "article", "title": "US approves new delivery of bombs and war planes to Israel amid protests \u2013 The Red Herald", "description": "The Land Day, Yom-al-Ard, was celebrated for the 48th time in Palestine and among the Palestinian diaspora all over the world on the 30th of March to commemorate protests against Israel confiscating 2,000 hectares of Palestinian lands in 1976", "modified time": "2024-03-30T22:23:14+00:00", "author": ["T.I."], "categories": ["Featured", "International"], "tags": ["Palestine", "Protests", "Repression", "Struggle for land"], "sections": ["Featured", "International", "Palestine", "Protests", "Repression", "Struggle for land", "English", "pll_660890d287d5c"], "source_name": "Red Herald"}